The paper deals with image super-resolution, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method proposed involves sparsity-based optimization, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also proposes a dictionary learning method, which is a topic in both machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
